prompts.frontCover: Front cover of a greeting card. A whimsical and humorous botanical illustration featuring cartoon versions of Lao Lao (person on the left in the photo) and Jordan (person on the right in the photo). They are depicted in a playful and exaggerated scene. Lao Lao is majestically riding on Jordan's back piggyback-style, holding the reins of a "saddle" made of woven leaves and vines as if he's a noble steed. Lao Lao has a joyful, laughing expression, wearing her white dress. Jordan has a comically strained but happy expression, as if he's giving it his all to carry her through a lush, magical forest. He is wearing his graduation gown and stole, but instead of a graduation cap, he wears a crown made of twigs and small flowers. The background is a dense, beautifully illustrated botanical paradise with oversized, fantastical plants, like glowing mushrooms, curly ferns, and drooping willow branches with tiny sparkling lights. A few whimsical forest critters, like a squirrel in a tiny party hat and a cheerful snail, watch them from the foliage. The entire scene is rendered in a charming, flat 2D art style with a soft, warm color palette. In the center of the image, floating amongst the leaves, the words "Happy Birthday to my favorite person to carry through life, Lao Lao" are written in an elegant, flowing, handwritten cursive script.
